channel.title: Java error! help!
channel.description:
[code] bash-4.0$ java TestGameDev Welcome to TestGame Developer Edition!
If you need help, say 'help'
[1]+ Stopped java TestGameDev bash-4.0$ help bash: help: command not found [1]+ Killed java TestGameDev [/code]
I get it running, It's compiled correctly, there's nothing wrong with my java! what's the problem? why does it keep on doing this?
-Thanks.
